Hi Casey,

The Pertronix is just another set of points so needs no different procedures to set the timing than normal points.

As for the spec of where to set the timing (5ATDC, TDC, 7.5BTDC etc) just use the same setting as for the 'normal' points.

Good luck
Bob Wallace
Bristol UK
1998 T2


